프로젝트 `D:\16. 자동화 도구\safeAutoTest`에서 작업합니다. `lib/site-types.ts`와 필요한 npm 패키지가 이미 설치돼 있습니다.

**목표:** `lib/url-normalizer.ts`와 `tests/unit/url-normalizer.test.ts`를 TDD로 생성하고 커밋합니다.

**규칙:**
- 이 두 파일만 건드리세요. 다른 파일 절대 수정 금지.
- 커밋까지 완료하세요.

---

**Step 1: `tests/unit/url-normalizer.test.ts` 생성**

```ts
import test from "node:test";
import assert from "node:assert/strict";
import { normalizeUrl, isHttpUrl, sameOrigin } from "../../lib/url-normalizer.ts";

test("lowercases protocol and host", () => {
  assert.equal(normalizeUrl("HTTPS://Example.COM/Path"), "https://example.com/Path");
});

test("strips fragment", () => {
  assert.equal(normalizeUrl("https://a.com/x#frag"), "https://a.com/x");
});

test("preserves query string", () => {
  assert.equal(normalizeUrl("https://a.com/x?b=2&a=1"), "https://a.com/x?b=2&a=1");
});

test("removes trailing slash except for root", () => {
  assert.equal(normalizeUrl("https://a.com/x/"), "https://a.com/x");
  assert.equal(normalizeUrl("https://a.com/"), "https://a.com/");
});

test("resolves relative against base", () => {
  assert.equal(normalizeUrl("/about", "https://a.com/home"), "https://a.com/about");
});

test("isHttpUrl: accepts http(s), rejects mailto/javascript/file", () => {
  assert.equal(isHttpUrl("https://a.com"), true);
  assert.equal(isHttpUrl("http://a.com"), true);
  assert.equal(isHttpUrl("mailto:x@y.com"), false);
  assert.equal(isHttpUrl("javascript:alert(1)"), false);
  assert.equal(isHttpUrl("file:///etc/passwd"), false);
});

test("sameOrigin honors allowSubdomains=false", () => {
  assert.equal(sameOrigin("https://a.com/x", "https://a.com/y", false), true);
  assert.equal(sameOrigin("https://a.com/x", "https://sub.a.com/y", false), false);
});

test("sameOrigin honors allowSubdomains=true", () => {
  assert.equal(sameOrigin("https://a.com/x", "https://sub.a.com/y", true), true);
  assert.equal(sameOrigin("https://a.com/x", "https://b.com/y", true), false);
});

test("returns null for malformed URL", () => {
  assert.equal(normalizeUrl("::::bad::::"), null);
});
```

**Step 2: 테스트 실패 확인**
```bash
cd "D:\16. 자동화 도구\safeAutoTest" && npx tsx --test tests/unit/url-normalizer.test.ts 2>&1 | head -10
```
"Cannot find module" 오류가 나야 정상.

**Step 3: `lib/url-normalizer.ts` 생성**

```ts
export function normalizeUrl(input: string, base?: string): string | null {
  try {
    const url = base ? new URL(input, base) : new URL(input);
    url.protocol = url.protocol.toLowerCase();
    url.hostname = url.hostname.toLowerCase();
    url.hash = "";
    if (url.pathname.length > 1 && url.pathname.endsWith("/")) {
      url.pathname = url.pathname.replace(/\/+$/, "");
    }
    return url.toString();
  } catch {
    return null;
  }
}

export function isHttpUrl(input: string): boolean {
  try {
    const protocol = new URL(input).protocol;
    return protocol === "http:" || protocol === "https:";
  } catch {
    return false;
  }
}

export function sameOrigin(a: string, b: string, allowSubdomains: boolean): boolean {
  try {
    const left = new URL(a);
    const right = new URL(b);
    if (left.protocol !== right.protocol) return false;
    if (allowSubdomains) {
      const leftRoot = left.hostname.split(".").slice(-2).join(".");
      const rightRoot = right.hostname.split(".").slice(-2).join(".");
      return leftRoot === rightRoot;
    }
    return left.host === right.host;
  } catch {
    return false;
  }
}
```

**Step 4: 테스트 통과 확인**
```bash
cd "D:\16. 자동화 도구\safeAutoTest" && npx tsx --test tests/unit/url-normalizer.test.ts 2>&1
```
9/9 PASS여야 합니다.

**Step 5: 커밋**
```bash
cd "D:\16. 자동화 도구\safeAutoTest" && git add lib/url-normalizer.ts tests/unit/url-normalizer.test.ts && git commit -m "feat(site): add url-normalizer with tests"
```

결과를 한 줄로 보고하세요: "PASS 9/9, committed" 또는 실패 내용.

